      "message": "Patch Set 6:\n\ntest 65 of replay-vbr is just a way for it to just mount and unmount right away, no actualtest being run like I said.\n\nI know this code does not change anything in osc, but it appears that this code triggers addition of something to osc lists that's not cleared later (I imagine something in osc code was copied over and forgotten to change some symbols?)\n\nWhen I remove this patch the crash is gone (let me try with the rebased one, though)",
