      "message": "Patch Set 6:\n\n(gdb) l *(lprocfs_remove_nolock+0x3b)\n0x2511b is in lprocfs_remove_nolock (/home/green/git/lustre-release/lustre/obdclass/lprocfs_status.c:397).\n392\t\n393\t        parent = root->parent;\n394\t        LASSERT(parent != NULL);\n395\t\n396\t        while (1) {\n397\t                while (temp->subdir != NULL)\n398\t                        temp = temp->subdir;\n399\t\n400\t                rm_entry = temp;\n401\t                temp = temp->parent;",
